text: Iyo ang Tondo Kanya ang Cavite () is a 1986 Filipino action movie directed by Pablo Santiago and stars Fernando Poe Jr., Ramon Revilla Sr., Anita Linda, Liza Lorena, Parquito Diaz, Berting Labra, Ruel Vernal, Romy Diaz, Vic Diaz, Max Alvarado. It was distributed by BSH Films. ==Other websites== * Category:1986 action movies Category:Filipino movies
